MUDitM Tests
============

test_max_children.c
  Verifies max-children connection limiting. Starts a TCP echo server,
  launches MUDitM with max-children=3, and checks that connections are
  capped, queued, and released correctly.

  Build:  cc -o test_max_children tests/test_max_children.c
  Run:    ./test_max_children [path-to-muditm]

  Defaults to ./muditm if no path is given. Requires no external
  dependencies beyond a C compiler and the muditm binary.
